quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,By the morning sunlight
  93,2,and the night when it falls still
  93,3,"Your Lord ˹O Prophet˺ has not abandoned you, nor has He become hateful ˹of you˺"
  93,4,And the next life is certainly far better for you than this one
  93,5,And ˹surely˺ your Lord will give so much to you that you will be pleased
  93,6,Did He not find you as an orphan then sheltered you
  93,7,Did He not find you unguided then guided you
  93,8,And did He not find you needy then satisfied your needs
  93,9,So do not oppress the orphan
  93,10,nor repulse the beggar
  93,11,And proclaim the blessings of your Lord